SUMMARY:Chapter 8 Quiz (8.1-8.5) - Requires Respondus LockDown Browser + We
 bcam [CCDM-114 N-DIC]
DESCRIPTION:Make sure to show work (as best as you can) when asked. I sugge
 st doing you work on a scratch sheet of paper and then transfer it onto th
 e computer using equation editor. The equation editor is the square root o
 f x icon (press the three dots icon to view the square root of x icon) and
  it allows you to use mathematical notation when needed. There is a video 
 below\, for more instruction in how to use the equation editor. If the equ
 ation editor is not an option\, please use your keyboard to write your ans
 wers.\n\nYou will need a laptop/computer with LockDown Browser to take thi
 s exam. A calculator as a cell phone and notes are NOT allowed and please\
 , note that that this exam will be timed. Do not submit the exam until you
  are completely done answering every question. There will be no re-takes o
 r corrections and the score you receive at the end of the exam is not your
  final score. There are questions that I need to grade by hand. As a resul
 t\, these questions will be marked as incorrect.\n\n[How to use Equation E
 ditor.mp4] (https://nmsu.instructure.com/courses/1310474/files/164634111/d
 ownload?wrap=1)\n\n 
CATEGORIES:work
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY
