DURATION:PT1H
SUMMARY:Grow with Google HSI Career Readiness Program  [COMM-1115G-M3H]
DESCRIPTION:--------------------------------------------------------\nCOMM1
 115G Grow with Google: HSI Career Readiness Program\n---------------------
 -----------------------------------\n\nHSI Career Readiness Program Assign
 ment\n---------------------------------------\n\nThe GwG program offers fi
 ve options called “pathways” from which you will complete 2 core lesso
 ns and then upload a screenshot to this assignment page. Most lessons incl
 ude watching a video lesson and then clicking “mark as complete” at th
 e bottom of the screen. For credit purposes\, you will need to take a scre
 enshot of the page after clicking “mark as complete” and upload the sc
 reenshot as a pdf or JPEG/JPG as proof of completion for credit.  \n\n \
 n\nYou will find the sign-up instructions that Google has provided below t
 hese instructions. This allows you to enroll in the SkillShop LMS so you c
 an access the lessons. You can choose any 2 core lessons you desire. Here 
 is a list of the pathways and core lessons: https://skillshop.exceedlms.co
 m/student/catalog/list?category_ids=6757-hsi-career-readiness-program \n\
 n \n\nSteps to get you started:\n\n1. Read the sign-up instructions (atta
 chment below)\n\n2. Once signed up\, click on the Grow with Google Career 
 Readiness Program link in the attachment\n\n3. Watch videos and/or complet
 e exercises in the desired core lesson\n\n4. Click “Mark as Complete” 
 when finished\n\n5. Screenshot and upload proof of completion into this Ca
 nvas assignment page.\n\n \n\nWe encourage you to complete at least one c
 ore lesson as soon as possible. Please let your GTA know if you have any q
 uestions.\n\nSign-up guide\n-------------\n\n[HSI Career Readiness Program
  sign-up guide.pdf] (https://nmsu.instructure.com/courses/1529739/files/21
 2514447?wrap=1)\n\nGrading\n-------\n\nYour completion of the criteria abo
 ve will gain you the points listed for this assignment. \n\nIf criteria a
 re NOT met you will receive the following point deductions:\n\n* 10% deduc
 tion up to 7 consecutive days the assignment is late. After 7 consecutive 
 days\, you will receive a zero. \n\n* 50% deduction for only submitting p
 roof of one lesson. \n\n 
CATEGORIES:work
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;UNTIL=20230512T235959Z
END:VEVENT
